  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is being done to determine the mechanism(s) contributing to the onset of symptoms&#xD;
      (i.e. shortness of breath and/or palpitations) as well as changes in right heart structure in&#xD;
      patients with Tetralogy of Fallot (TOF).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
