      <textblock>
        This will be a prospective study of patients with repaired Tetralogy of Fallot (TOF) and&#xD;
        pulmonary regurgitation (PR) receiving care at Mayo Clinic Rochester, MN.&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Moderate (or greater) PR based on quantitative Doppler echocardiography.&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Repaired TOF&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Pregnant Women&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Unable to undergo CMRI&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
